---
title: Mexican Spiced Beef Tortillas with kidney beans and zesty creme fraiche
description: Bring a taste of Mexico to your table tonight with these simple to assemble meaty tortillas. The zesty creme fraiche topping is the perfect pairing for the lightly spiced bean, bell pepper and beef filling.
